wikipedia_page.main: Vice Admiral Sir John Morrison Webster KCB (3 November 1932 – 5 October 2020) was a Royal Navy officer who became Flag Officer Plymouth and Port Admiral, Devonport.

response: John Webster (c. 1580–c. 1634) was an English dramatist and contemporary of William Shakespeare.
